+------------------------------------------------------------------------------
+--                                                                          --
+--                  GNAT RUN-TIME LIBRARY (GNARL) COMPONENTS                --
+--                                                                          --
+--                   S Y S T E M . O S _ I N T E R F A C E                  --
+--                                                                          --
+--                                   S p e c                                --
